---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Result Marketing - AI-Powered SEO Agency"
  description="Learn how Result Marketing helps Malaysian businesses get better SEO results using AI automation. Founded by Jacob Ng in 2023."
  locale={lang}
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="section bg-gradient-mesh">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <span class="text-accent-500 font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 block">About Us</span>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black mb-6 text-white">
          Better SEO Results in Less Time at Lower Prices
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-secondary-400 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Founded by Jacob Ng in 2023, Result Marketing uses AI tools like Claude Code to speed up SEO work. We give you better results faster because AI does the repetitive work while humans focus on strategy.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Story -->
  <section class="section bg-dark">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-8 text-center text-white gradient-text">How Result Marketing Started</h2>
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none prose-invert">
          <p>
            In 2023, Jacob Ng was exploring AI-powered SEO. A friend invited him to join an AI SEO courseâ€”and this friend happened to run a money lending business called Ing Heng Credit.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong class="text-accent-pink">The problem:</strong> Ing Heng Credit specializes in equipment financing. They compete directly with banks. And when people ask ChatGPT about equipment financing, banks usually get mentioned first.
          </p>
          <p>
            Jacob saw an opportunity. He offered to help Ing Heng dominate AI search engines using AIEO (AI Engine Optimization).
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>The strategy:</strong> Instead of just one language, Jacob built SEO in 3 languages (English, Malay, Chinese). This massive coverage meant ChatGPT started mentioning Ing Heng Credit <em>before</em> banks.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>The result:</strong> Ing Heng started getting 1-2 qualified leads per day from AI search engines. The owner was super happy with the service.
          </p>
          <p>
            That's when Jacob realized something important: <strong>service businesses will be powered by AI sooner or later.</strong> Those who adapt early will win. Those who don't will lose to competitors.
          </p>
          <p>
            Jacob made a decision. He told all his clients: <strong>Quit WordPress.</strong> WordPress wasn't built for AI search engines. Instead, he started building SEO-optimized websites using raw code with AIâ€”clean, fast, and designed for AI engines to love.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>The mission:</strong> Cut costs lower than hiring one admin staff. Make AI-powered SEO affordable for every business.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Here's the difference:</strong><br>
            Traditional SEO: A human can test 1 or 2 ideas per month.<br>
            <span class="text-success-500 font-bold">AI-powered SEO:</span> We can test 100 variations and find the winner faster.
          </p>
          <p>
            That's how Result Marketing was bornâ€”real results from a real client, not theory.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Values -->
  <section class="section bg-secondary-900">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-4 text-white">Why Clients Choose Us</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-secondary-400">
          Four reasons why businesses work with Result Marketing instead of traditional SEO agencies.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        {values.map(value => (
          <div class="card card-hover">
            <div class="text-5xl mb-4">{value.icon}</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-3 text-white">{value.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-secondary-400">{value.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Timeline -->
  <section class="section bg-dark">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-4 text-white">Our Journey: From One Client to Many</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-secondary-400">
          How a successful case study with Ing Heng Credit led to a full AI-powered SEO service.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          {milestones.map((milestone, index) => (
            <div class="flex gap-6">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 to-primary-800 text-white font-black text-lg flex items-center justify-center glow-purple">
                  {milestone.year}
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex-1 pt-2">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-2 text-white">{milestone.title}</h3>
                <p class="text-secondary-400">{milestone.description}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team Section -->
  <section class="section bg-gradient-mesh">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-4 text-white">Meet the Team</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-secondary-400">
          Small team that knows how to use AI tools to deliver big results for clients.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        {team.map(member => (
          <div class="card card-hover text-center">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 to-primary-800 mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-4xl font-black glow-purple">
              {member.name.split(' ').map(n => n[0]).join('')}
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-1 text-white">{member.name}</h3>
            <p class="text-primary-500 font-bold mb-3">{member.role}</p>
            <p class="text-secondary-400 mb-4">{member.description}</p>
            <div class="flex justify-center gap-3">
              {member.social.linkedin && (
                <a href={member.social.linkedin} class="text-secondary-500 hover:text-primary-500 transition-colors" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 0h-14c-2.761 0-5 2.239-5 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.762 0 5-2.239 5-5v-14c0-2.761-2.238-5-5-5zm-11 19h-3v-11h3v11zm-1.5-12.268c-.966 0-1.75-.79-1.75-1.764s.784-1.764 1.75-1.764 1.75.79 1.75 1.764-.783 1.764-1.75 1.764zm13.5 12.268h-3v-5.604c0-3.368-4-3.113-4 0v5.604h-3v-11h3v1.765c1.396-2.586 7-2.777 7 2.476v6.759z"/></svg>
                </a>
              )}
              {member.social.twitter && (
                <a href={member.social.twitter} class="text-secondary-500 hover:text-primary-500 transition-colors" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M24 4.557c-.883.392-1.832.656-2.828.775 1.017-.609 1.798-1.574 2.165-2.724-.951.564-2.005.974-3.127 1.195-.897-.957-2.178-1.555-3.594-1.555-3.179 0-5.515 2.966-4.797 6.045-4.091-.205-7.719-2.165-10.148-5.144-1.29 2.213-.669 5.108 1.523 6.574-.806-.026-1.566-.247-2.229-.616-.054 2.281 1.581 4.415 3.949 4.89-.693.188-1.452.232-2.224.084.626 1.956 2.444 3.379 4.6 3.419-2.07 1.623-4.678 2.348-7.29 2.04 2.179 1.397 4.768 2.212 7.548 2.212 9.142 0 14.307-7.721 13.995-14.646.962-.695 1.797-1.562 2.457-2.549z"/></svg>
                </a>
              )}
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="section bg-gradient-mesh">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="card-disruptive p-12 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-4 text-white">
          Want Better SEO Results at Lower Prices?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl mb-8 text-secondary-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Let's talk about your business goals. We will explain how AI tools can help you get more customers from search engines.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="https://wa.me/60175032281?text=Hi%2C%20I%27m%20interested%20in%20Result%20Marketing%20services." target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary">
            Contact Us
          </a>
          <a href="/en/services" class="btn btn-secondary">
            Our Services
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
